                     <interp inst="t17831210-59-person719" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I produce the Roebuck book, it is there spelt 
               <persName id="t17831210-59-person720">
                  Shaw
                   Ferguson
               <interp inst="t17831210-59-person720" type="surname" value="Ferguson"></interp>
