               <p>I am clerk to the treasurer of the navy, for paying seamens wages at Chatham.</p>
               <p>Did you ever see the prisoner? - I cannot call to my mind that I have, I have paid so many thousands of pounds since, I cannot recollect: a person came to the Pay-Office by the name of 
               <persName id="t17831210-59-person733">
                  Robert
                   Dewar
               <interp inst="t17831210-59-person733" type="surname" value="Dewar"></interp>
