                     <interp inst="t17831210-59-person762" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             is not dead now, I have a letter I received from him: I have ten witnesses that can prove that.</p>
               <p>Court. Who said so? - 
               <persName id="t17831210-59-person763">
                  Gregor
                   Farquharson
               <interp inst="t17831210-59-person763" type="surname" value="Farquharson"></interp>
